Japanese Overlay for RStudio Desktop
====================================

This repository contains only the overlay scripts, CSS, and JavaScript authored
for this project. It does not contain RStudio Desktop, Posit binaries, RStudio
source code, Posit logos, RStudio logos, or official distribution archives.

RStudio Desktop is a product of Posit Software, PBC and is licensed separately.
The upstream RStudio source repository states that RStudio is licensed under
the GNU Affero General Public License version 3 (AGPLv3), with license terms in
the upstream COPYING file.

Posit, RStudio, and Shiny are trademarks of Posit Software, PBC, all rights
reserved, and may be registered in the United States Patent and Trademark Office
and in other countries. This project is unofficial and is not endorsed by,
sponsored by, or affiliated with Posit Software, PBC.

Users should download RStudio Desktop only from official Posit distribution
locations. The setup scripts in this repository download an official xcopy
build locally and apply this overlay on the user's machine.
